text.tspan: In the XAMPP control panel, press the Start button beside the MySQL since that's the only feature we
will be using for now. After clicking, check that the status of MySQL is green to ensure that it is running
properly. Ask a mentor for help if a yellow or red colour appears instead.
Insde the bin folder, find the mysql.exe file and press double click on your mouse to open it. This will
open a console terminal that we will use to create databases.
